DataCenterSystem - Class in ui
The class DataCenterSystem will be the user interface of the system, through this the object corresponding to the data center will be instantiated with the attributes that the user enters, also a menu with the following functions will be shown: List available mini-rooms Rent a mini-room Cancel a mini-room rental Show the data center map Simulate all mini-rooms lighting Simulate mini-rooms shutdown Exit to the system And depending on the option or function that the user chooses to do the class will call the method that will perform it.
